#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:2
msgid "严格模式"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:6
msgid ""
"在ES5中，除了正常的运行模式之外，添加了严格模式（strict "
"mode），这种模式使得代码显式地脱离“马虎模式/稀松模式/懒散模式“（sloppy）模式在更严格的条件下运行。严格模式不仅仅是一个子集：它的产生是为了形成与正常代码不同的语义。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:8
msgid "引入严格模式的目的主要是："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:10
msgid "通过抛出错误来消除了一些原有静默错误"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:11
msgid "消除JavaScript语法的一些不合理、不严谨之处，减少一些怪异行为"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:12
msgid "消除代码运行的一些不安全之处，保证代码运行的安全"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:13
msgid "修复了一些导致 JavaScript引擎难以执行优化的缺陷，提高编译器效率，增加运行速度"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:14
msgid "禁用了在ECMAScript的未来版本中可能会定义的一些语法，为未来新版本的JavaScript做铺垫"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:17
msgid "调用"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:18
msgid ""
"严格模式使用 ``\"use strict\";`` 字符串开启。对整个脚本文件而言，可以将 ``\"use strict\"`` "
"放在脚本文件的第一行使整个脚本以严格模式运行。如果这行语句不在第一行则不会生效，会以正常模式运行。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:20
msgid "对单个函数而言，将 ``\"use strict\"`` 放在函数体的第一行，则整个函数以严格模式运行。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:23
msgid "行为改变"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:24
msgid "在严格模式中，主要有以下的行为更改："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:27
msgid "全局变量显式声明"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:28
msgid "在正常模式中，如果一个变量没有声明就赋值，默认是全局变量。严格模式禁止这种用法，全局变量必须显式声明。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:37
msgid "禁止使用with语句"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:38
msgid "with语句无法在编译时就确定，属性到底归属哪个对象，这会影响编译效率，所以在严格模式中被禁止。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:41
msgid "创设eval作用域"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:42
msgid "正常模式下，eval语句的作用域，取决于它处于全局作用域，还是处于函数作用域。严格模式下，eval语句本身就是一个作用域，不再能够生成全局变量了，它所生成的变量只能用于eval内部。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:45
msgid "禁止删除变量"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:46
msgid "严格模式下无法删除变量。只有configurable设置为true的对象属性，才能被删除。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:49
msgid "显式报错"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:50
msgid "正常模式下一些错误只会默默地失败，但是严格模式下将会报错，包括以下几种场景："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:52
msgid "对一个对象的只读属性进行赋值"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:53
msgid "对一个使用getter方法读取的属性进行赋值"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:54
msgid "对禁止扩展的对象添加新属性"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:55
msgid "删除一个不可删除的属性"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:58
msgid "语法错误"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:59
msgid "严格模式新增了一些语法错误，包括："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:61
msgid "对象不能有重名的属性"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:62
msgid "函数不能有重名的参数"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:63
msgid "禁止八进制表示法"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:64
msgid "函数必须声明在顶层"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:65
msgid "新增保留字"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:66
msgid "class"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:67
msgid "enum"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:68
msgid "export"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:69
msgid "extends"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:70
msgid "import"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:71
msgid "super"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:74
msgid "安全增强"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:75
msgid "禁止this关键字指向全局对象"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:76
msgid "禁止在函数内部遍历调用栈"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:79
msgid "限制arguments对象"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:80
msgid "不允许对arguments赋值"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:81
msgid "arguments不再追踪参数的变化"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/language/javascript/strict.rst:82
msgid "禁止使用arguments.callee"
msgstr ""
